tvshowdetails.label: Hell on Wheels
tvshowdetails.plot: Hell on Wheels tells the epic story of post-Civil War America, focusing on a Confederate soldier (Mount) who sets out to exact revenge on the Union soldiers who have killed his wife. His journey takes him west to Hell on Wheels, a dangerous, raucous, lawless melting pot of a town that travels with and services the construction of the first transcontinental railroad, an engineering feat unprecedented for its time.
tvshowdetails.title: Hell on Wheels

1.label: 1x01. Pilot
1.plot: A former confederate soldier journeys to the transcontinental railroad to seek vengeance.
1.title: Pilot

1.label: 1x02. Immoral Mathematics
1.plot: Lily encounters natives in the wilderness. Cullen is questioned in regards to his recent actions against others. Meanwhile, Durant continues his push for political gain through his persuasions.
1.title: Immoral Mathematics

1.label: 1x03. A New Birth of Freedom
1.plot: When Lily goes missing, Durant organizes a search party. A subsidiary request prevents Cullen from his continued search for the sergeant involved in the murder of his wife.
1.title: A New Birth of Freedom

1.label: 1x04. Jamais Je Ne T'oublierai
1.plot: Cullen's search for the sergeant nears its end; Durant keeps to his hidden agenda while assisting in Lily's recuperation.
1.title: Jamais Je Ne T'oublierai

1.label: 1x05. Bread and Circuses
1.plot: A bare-knuckle brouhaha between Elam and Cullen is spurred by Durant's latest attempt to deal with the railroad's financial crisis.
1.title: Bread and Circuses

1.label: 1x06. Pride, Pomp and Circumstance
1.plot: Durant challenges the Cheyenne to a competition in an effort to bring a halt to ongoing negotiations. Meanwhile, Elam and Cullen try to prevent bloodshed in town.
1.title: Pride, Pomp and Circumstance

1.label: 1x07. Revelations
1.plot: With Elam's life in the balance, Cullen must decide how much he’s willing to risk. Meanwhile Durant faces financial ruin as Lily confronts the family of her late husband.
1.title: Revelations

1.label: 1x08. Derailed
1.plot: Durant dispatches Cullen and Elam on a mission of vengeance. Lily struggles to find her place.
1.title: Derailed

1.label: 1x09. Timshel
1.plot: A looming railroad deadline throws Cullen and Lily together; Joseph and Elam deal with what their violent mission has wrought.
1.title: Timshel

1.label: 1x10. God of Chaos
1.plot: In the Season 1 finale, Cullen's past and future collide, impacting his life on the railroad.
1.title: God of Chaos
